  <div class="venn-section">
    <div class="venn-eyebrow">Why each player engages</div>
    <h2 class="venn-title">Three actors. One platform around them.</h2>
    <p class="venn-intro">Patient, commissioner and supplier each have different reasons to engage. They overlap with each other in specific pairs, and they all share one centre: the service has to actually work, safely, and to be trusted. <strong>NHSE / HomeTest is the platform that holds it all together.</strong> Not a fourth player: the environment in which the three relate. <strong>Aisha, David and Ngozi are part of that platform</strong>: Aisha IS the clinical framework, David IS the commercial framework, Ngozi IS the information governance framework. The platform is the sum of those three layers, not a separate thing alongside them.</p>

