        <div class="vl"><div class="vl-h vl-pc">Health outcomes live between Patient &amp; Commissioner.</div>This is the NHS mission expressed in pairs. Equity, access at scale, the population-level reasons commissioners spend money, the personal reasons patients use the service. Both sides of the same coin.</div>
        <div class="vl"><div class="vl-h vl-cs">Economics live between Commissioner &amp; Supplier.</div>Not in the patient&apos;s experience, but the foundation that lets it exist. Pricing, payment, risk, value for money. If the economics don&apos;t work for both sides, the service doesn&apos;t get bought, doesn&apos;t get built, doesn&apos;t reach the patient at all.</div>
