        <div class="vl"><div class="vl-h" style="color:#005EB8;">Ngozi is part of the platform: the information governance framework.</div>Ngozi doesn't sit inside any one circle either. She is part of the NHSE/HomeTest envelope: the DPIA, the DSA, the controller designation rules, the lawful basis position. Every data flow in the service crosses her framework. Without her layer, the service cannot lawfully process patient data at all.</div>
